COMS- 327 
Assignment 1.10/2 - Choose Your Own Assignment
Esha Gadgil


The game features automatic ship placement, weather effects, sound effects, and customizable board sizes and ship configurations.

This is an implementation of a battleship game in C++.

To make open terminal and type main and then run ./battleships.


Choose number of ships , size and their location 

Then the player and computer AI takes turns targetting each others board.

Use this format for placing ships 0 0 V
And this format to attack 0 0 
